# Zecruu Games - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
Online gaming platform with Texas Hold'em Poker and Dots Survivor games.

## Lessons
- Branch name is `master`, not `main`
- Use semicolons in PowerShell to chain commands (not `&&`)
- Server runs on port 3001 (production) or 3002 (local dev)

